document_data.caption: A map showing Whitefish Alley in Aithelar.
document_data.name: Whitefish Alley
document_data.mainbody: '''Whitefish Alley''' was a small street found in the coastal town of [[Aithelar]] in [[Callidyrr]] on the [[Moonshae Isles]] in the {{YearlinkName|1345}}.{{Cite interactive atlas}}
document_data.Location: Whitefish Alley began at [[Bottle Lane]] and ended in an alley on the east side of Aithelar. The street crossed [[Aithe High Street]] near its center.
